%h2
  Subscribed!

%p
  Your email
  %code
    = recipient.email
  has been added to the list
  = succeed '.' do
    = "##{list.id}"
  Your position in the list is
  = succeed '.' do
    = "##{list.recipients.count}"

%p
  If you want to unsubscribe,
  = succeed '.' do
    %a{href: '/unsubscribe?token=' + CGI.escape(token)} click here

